Log Configuration

	This configuration file manages the system logs. User can change the log levels between 'DEBUG', 'INFO', 'WARN', 'ERROR', 'FATAL'. The log file
	can be found in /configuration/log.json. This can be modified using GUI as well.
	
+-----+
"logLevel" : "DEBUG" ,

	"configuration" : {
		  		"appenders" : [
		               { "type" : "console" }    		      	    
		  			          ]
		      		}
+-----+
